# Pages & routing — Zeroindex

- **`DocsLayout`:** Used for home, blog listing, changelog listing, team listing, docs, tags, and many system pages. It wraps `BaseLayout` with `hideNav` and `hideFooter` and provides `Sidebar` + mobile/desktop top bars.
- **`BaseLayout`:** Full-site chrome (`Navigation`, `Footer`, `BaseHead`, global CSS). Use when you intentionally want the marketing nav/footer, or extend via other layouts that import it.
- **Dynamic segments:**
  - `src/pages/docs/[...slug].astro` — URL `/docs/{doc.id}` (sorted by `category` + `order`).
  - `src/pages/blog/[page].astro` — paginated index `/blog/1`, …; `astro.config.mjs` redirects `/blog` → `/blog/1`.
  - `src/pages/blog/posts/[...slug].astro` — `/blog/posts/{post.id}`; uses `BlogLayout` + prev/next by pubDate.
  - `src/pages/blog/tags/[tag].astro` — `/blog/tags/{tag}`.
  - `src/pages/integrations/[...slug].astro` — `/integrations/{id}`.
  - `src/pages/changelog/[...slug].astro` — `/changelog/{id}`.
  - `src/pages/team/[...slug].astro` — `/team/{id}`; missing entry redirects to `/404`.
  - `src/pages/legal/[...slug].astro` — `/legal/{id}`.

- **Cards build URLs:** e.g. `BlogCard` → `/blog/posts/` + post id; `ChangelogCard` → `/changelog/` + id; `IntegrationsCard` → `/integrations/` + id; `TeamCard` → `/team/` + id. If you change URL shapes, update these components and any hardcoded links.

- **Reference:** `/system/overview` embeds a route matrix (verify against `src/pages/`; some listed URLs may not exist in this checkout).
